{
  "id": "censure-road-camp-voss",
  "title": "Preceptor Voss",
  "nodes": {
    "start": {
      "lines": [
        "Preceptor Voss has slates pinned under one boot and mud on both cuffs.",
        "\"If Caldus calls this a camp again, make him count latrine nails. A camp has rest. This has paperwork with damp corners.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Fill the Hallowfen route report",
          "next": "report-briefing"
        },
        {
          "label": "Ask about cult-breaker training",
          "next": "training"
        },
        {
          "label": "Ask how supplies move",
          "next": "supplies"
        },
        {
          "label": "Ask about the filed report",
          "conditions": {
            "flag": "censure-road-voss-report-perfect"
          },
          "next": "report-filed"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave Voss to the slates",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "training": {
      "lines": [
        "\"New breakers learn bells before blades. A missed bell wastes a squad before the enemy gets a turn.\"",
        "\"After that, they learn how to stand still while a farmer begs for mercy with someone else's mouth.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Leave Voss to the drill yard",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "supplies": {
      "lines": [
        "\"Runa issues what the writ allows. Maev sells what the writ forgot. Everyone calls that corruption until they need dry beans.\"",
        "\"The road survives on doctrine, wax seals, and people pretending the third column in the ledger does not exist.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Leave Voss to the ledgers",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "report-filed": {
      "lines": [
        "\"Your report survived the red pencil. That does not make you holy, but it does make you rare.\"",
        "\"Maev has your issue bundle. If she argues, tell her I can count her beans louder than she can sell them.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Leave Voss to the filed slates",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
    "report-briefing": {
      "lines": [
        "Voss pulls a damp packet from beneath her boot and clips it to a field board.",
        "\"Hallowfen route report, Form C-17. Thirty questions. One answer each. Circle answer one down the rest if you want the paper to know you surrendered.\""
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "label": "Take the field board",
          "next": "report-q01"
        },
        {
          "label": "Leave the report for now",
          "close": true
        }
      ]
    },
